to\u2011day crew interaction on long\u2011haul flights.\n- What would change my vote: Convincing evidence that Candidate\u202fA\u2019s unfriendly/unorganized behavior is minor and does not impact safety, or that Candidate\u202fB\u2019s uncooperative behavior is occasional and manageable, or that Candidate\u202fD\u2019s arrogance does not affect crew dynamics.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}", "thoughts": "We need to produce final public message as per format. We are agent_3. According to internal memory, we currently support Candidate C. The group appears unanimous on Candidate C (agents 1,2,3 all now vote C). We need to see if any new info suggests change. No new info beyond what we have. So we keep Candidate C. Provide reasoning summary similar to previous but must be concise. Provide confidence/uncertainty moderate. Provide METADATA_JSON with vote \"Candidate C\"."}
